# Day 01 - Enterprise Active Directory Lab

## Objective
Built a fully functional enterprise identity environment using Windows Server 2022 and Windows 10 client.

## Key Components
- Domain Controller (DC01)
- Active Directory Domain Services (AD DS)
- DNS Configuration
- Organizational Units (OU Structure)
- User & Group Management
- Domain Join (Client Machine)

## Network Configuration
- DC01: 192.168.56.10
- Client: 192.168.56.20
- Host-only network

## Key Skills Demonstrated
- Active Directory setup and management
- DNS configuration
- Identity and access management (IAM)
- Privilege assignment (Domain Admins)
- Network troubleshooting (ping validation)
- Domain integration

## Outcome
Successfully deployed and validated a working enterprise domain environment with authenticated client access.
